    "body": "Problem:\r\n\"Sorry\" in a message (1) is noise, and (2) actually reduces the clarity of the message because it the titlecasing of \"Sorry\" distracts from the actually important part of the message.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nDrop \"Sorry\" from messages.\r\n\r\n",
